dcterms:description: The ImageNet VID dataset is the largest dataset for temporal object detection, requiring algorithms to detect 30-class targets in consecutive frames, with 4000 videos in the training set and 555 videos in the validation set.
dcterms:title: ImageNet VID

dcterms:description: The 2DMOT15 dataset is a multi-object tracking dataset consisting of 11 training sequences, with annotations available only for the training set, and is used to evaluate tracking performance.
dcterms:title: 2DMOT15
